      "paddingTop": "l",
      "paddingTopLarge": "2xl",
      "content": [
        {
          "renderType": "container",
          "maxWidth": "xs",
          "richTextStyles": true,
          "content": [
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "h2",
              "content": "The Project"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Redesign and develop the Injury Board website."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "h3",
              "content": "The Brief"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Context"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "The Injury Board was in the process of changing its rules of membership, particularly its system of acceptance and wanted the site to reflect this new direction. They wanted the new site to convey to users that members form an exclusive group made up of the best of the best and ultimately instill trust. Naturally, stakeholders voiced a desire for the site to stand-out in an elegant way."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Overall, they wanted the redesign to make the site simpler, particularly the directory of firms and members. This not only applied to the back-end too. The existing site was built on a legacy framework that was becoming burdensome to manage. Creating a better experience for internal users to manage and update the site was also important."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Goals"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "ul",
              "content": [
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Convey to users exclusivity of membership and trustworthiness of Injury Board"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Simplify the site, especially dated and clunky directory of firms and members"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Create an easier to manage back-end"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Guiding Keywords"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "From this brief and conversations with stakeholders we captured these keywords to use as our focus throughout all phases of the project:"
            }
