          "content": [
            {
              "renderType": "richText",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Creating a stand-out experience with the use of animations and transitions expressed by stakeholders also formed a key part of the implementation stage. Reveals and subtle fades when elements were visible in the viewport were used to complement the content and elegant look we were seeking to achieve while not being distracting or overdone."
